Definition: a microscope that is similar in purpose to a light microscope but achieves much greater resolving power by using a parallel beam of electrons to illuminate the object instead of a beam of light
Synonyms: microscope, a, that, is, similar, in, purpose, to, light, but, achieves, much, greater, resolving, power, by, using, parallel, beam, of, electrons, illuminate, the, object, instead
Category: noun.artifact
